<b>Here.</b>

5
00:00:23,960 --> 00:00:27,430
<b>Are you sure you want to stay at your current school?</b>

6
00:00:27,900 --> 00:00:29,870
<b>I'd rather just take the bull by the horns...</b>

7
00:00:30,940 --> 00:00:32,470
<b>than to try and adjust somewhere new.</b>

8
00:00:32,900 --> 00:00:35,040
<b>It looks like you've mustered up your courage.</b>

9
00:00:35,910 --> 00:00:37,310
<b>And for that, I'm grateful.</b>

10
00:01:03,630 --> 00:01:05,370
<b>- Hey, Dad. - You're home.</b>

11
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:07,810
<b>Hey, guys. Gosh, it smells delicious.</b>

12
00:01:08,710 --> 00:01:12,380
<b>My goodness, it's grilled fish, my favorite.</b>

13
00:01:13,610 --> 00:01:14,950
<b>I'm starving.</b>

14
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:16,950
<b>Wash your hands first.</b>

15
00:01:17,550 --> 00:01:19,050
<b>I'll scoop the rice for you.</b>

16
00:01:19,650 --> 00:01:21,020
<b>Gosh, why can't you do a better job?</b>

17
00:01:21,020 --> 00:01:22,990
<b>How is that you're always getting scolded by Mom?</b>

18
00:01:24,090 --> 00:01:28,460
<b>That's just because your mom loves me way too much.</b>

19
00:01:28,630 --> 00:01:31,500
<b>- Whatever. - Yes, he's right about that.</b>

20
00:01:34,370 --> 00:01:35,500
<b>See?</b>

21
00:01:37,700 --> 00:01:38,840
<b>Look at his face.</b>

22
00:01:39,270 --> 00:01:40,710
<b>- Let's eat. I'm hungry. - Okay.</b>

23
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:43,880
<b>It's good.</b>

24
00:01:45,480 --> 00:01:46,940
<b>Did anything special happen in school?</b>

25
00:01:47,250 --> 00:01:49,980
<b>- School is always the same. - How was your day, honey?</b>

26
00:01:52,520 --> 00:01:54,790
<b>I'm going on a business trip to China next Tuesday.</b>

27
00:01:55,350 --> 00:01:58,260
<b>Really? Can we expect some good news?</b>

28
00:01:58,360 --> 00:02:01,360
<b>I have a really good feeling about this one.</b>

29
00:02:02,260 --> 00:02:04,800
<b>I guess he really might get the deal this time.</b>

30
00:02:05,600 --> 00:02:07,370
<b>What are you going to get for me in China?</b>

31
00:02:07,370 --> 00:02:10,840
<b>What do you want? What should I get for you?</b>

32
00:02:11,140 --> 00:02:12,670
<b>All I need is you, Dad.</b>

33
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,510
<b>I'm impressed, Joon Young.</b>

34
00:02:17,110 --> 00:02:18,580
<b>All I need is your mom.</b>

35
00:02:31,290 --> 00:02:32,420
<b>I'm done.</b>

36
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,690
<b>Okay, go and get some rest.</b>

